title: Global photo printing and merchandising market value 2016 and 2021
yAxis: Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 2.
In general Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 2016 to 2021.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2021.
The highest Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars, of value 19.09 was reached at Year 2021
Minimum Market revenue in billion U.S. dollars about 14.5 was reached at Year 2016
